<p><em>Note: I tidied up my garden about three weeks ago, and I had a lot of old garden equipment taking up space in the garden shed. Plus I had to dispose of this garden waste properly. Today's test is primarily going to be aimed at improving or repairing the gardening equipment. Due to the number of blades on some of the equipment. I've prepared a few potted shrubs to test the results and I've requisitioned Kevlar armour for both myself and D-51215 in case of potential stabbing injuries.</em></p>
